      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <em>PPZO9410</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Price</b> 100 gp; <b>Weight</b> 5 lbs.</p>\r\n<p>This thick, heavily padded sleeve fits over the wearer's arm and serves as a target for <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Animal\">animals</a> being trained to attack. When used in conjunction with the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/handle-animal\">Handle Animal</a> skill to train an <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Animal\">animal</a> for a general purpose, this item grants the user a +5 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Competence-Bonus\">competence bonus</a> on her <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/handle-animal\">Handle Animal</a> check to successfully combat train an <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Animal\">animal</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n"
